events.event_name: Freddie Mac Weekly Mortgage Rate Release
events.description: The release of the average 30-year fixed mortgage rate for the week ending February 5th.

facts.fact_text: The average rate on a 30-year fixed mortgage rose to 6.11% as of February 5th.

evidences.evidence_text: The average rate on a 30-year fixed mortgage rose marginally to 6.11% as of February 5th

facts.fact_text: Mortgage rates have increased for three consecutive weeks.
